metadata.label: Description
metadata.value: This album consists of photographs, travel permits, newspaper clippings, and other documents related to the Legendre Iran Expedition for the American Museum of Natural History. Photos show Gertrude and Sidney Legendre camping and hunting with George Goodwin from the Museum.

metadata.label: Series
value: Gertrude Sanford Legendre Papers: Scrapbooks and Photo Albums

metadata.label: Digitization Specifications
metadata.value: 400 dpi, 24-bit depth, color, Bookeye 4V1, Archival masters are tiffs.
